Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.30,0:01:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Hana?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.56,0:01:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.62,0:01:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost to the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana!
